          },
          "activation_name": "Break Free",
          "effect": "Spend a Mythic Point; *Freedom\u2019s Flame* blazes with a rose-red light, creating a beacon of spiritual strength. Any creature within 120 feet that\u2019s currently under a compulsion or control effect can immediately attempt a new saving throw to break free of the effect, with a +3 status bonus.",
